ER24&#8217;s Russel Meiring said paramedics arrived on the scene around 8am on Monday and found the bodies in a veld outside of an estate near Centurion.&#8220;It would appear that the three patients were bound gagged and burned to death but is subject to postmortem and law enforcement investigation &#8221; he said.Meiring said all three people had already died due to their injuries and paramedics couldn&#8217;t do anything to help them.&#8220;Nothing could be done for them and they were declared dead on the scene &#8221; he said.Meiring said police were on the scene for further investigation.